    "description": "Using AI to create content is becoming the norm.\n\nYou can hate it all you want...\nBut that's how it is.\n\nText-based content is easy.\nThe challenge is graphics, images and video.\n\nI'm heavy on visual-first content!\nAnd there is one AI tool I use extensively.\n\n✨ It's Kling AI.\n\nA lot of people think of AI-generated images and videos as \"AI slop\" - low-effort junk.\n\nAnd here's the thing...\n\nIn order to create amazing visuals, you need to inject your creativity, your brand, and your personal touch.\n\nBut you can still:\n- \"Steal\" like an artist\n- Use AI to assist you\n\nLet me show you what I mean.",
